-- Arsenal Signs Ozil From Real Madrid for Club Record Sum
-- B y   C h r i s t o p h e r   E l s e r
-- 2013-09-02T21:39:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-09-02/arsenal-signs-ozil-from-real-madrid-for-club-record-sum.html
Arsenal signed German international
midfielder Mesut Ozil from Real Madrid for a record sum for the
English Premier League soccer club.  The 24-year-old will join the north London team after
signing a long-term contract, Arsenal said today in a statement.  Ozil made 159 appearances in three years for the Spanish
team and won the league and Spanish cup during his stay.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Christopher Elser at 
 celser@bloomberg.net  